<!-- v0.30.5.2213 — LOVB TOOLKIT · the 4 decision tools surfaced upfront -->
<section class="lovb-section lovb-toolkit-section">
  <div class="lovb-section-eyebrow">// THE TOOLKIT · DECIDE BEFORE YOU SIGN</div>
  <h2 class="lovb-section-h">Four tools. <span class="serif">One decision.</span></h2>
  <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2.5px;color:var(--gold,#d4af37);font-weight:700;margin-top:6px;margin-bottom:12px;text-align:center">// POWERED BY FIELDCHECK IQ</div>
  <p class="lovb-section-sub">Score the pro projection. Find your archetype match. Read the market fit. Spot the roster gap. Each tool is one click. Methodology cited. Free to use.</p>

  <div class="lovb-toolkit-grid">
    <a class="lovb-tool-card" href="/lovb/projection">
      <div class="lovb-tool-card-eyebrow">// IQ SCORE</div>
      <h3 class="lovb-tool-card-h">Projection.</h3>
      <p class="lovb-tool-card-sub">8-dimensional score · position-weighted · 5 presets. Quantify a player's LOVB readiness before the contract conversation.</p>
      <span class="lovb-tool-card-cta">Score a player →</span>
    </a>
    <a class="lovb-tool-card" href="/lovb/match">
      <div class="lovb-tool-card-eyebrow">// IQ MATCH</div>
      <h3 class="lovb-tool-card-h">Archetype match.</h3>
      <p class="lovb-tool-card-sub">Cosine similarity against the entire LOVB founding cohort. Find the closest comparables and their actual pro outcomes.</p>
      <span class="lovb-tool-card-cta">Match the archetype →</span>
    </a>
    <a class="lovb-tool-card" href="/lovb/fit">
      <div class="lovb-tool-card-eyebrow">// IQ FIT</div>
      <h3 class="lovb-tool-card-h">Market fit.</h3>
      <p class="lovb-tool-card-sub">Weighted scoring across 6 markets (Austin, Salt Lake, Atlanta, Houston, Nebraska, Madison). Where does this player actually fit?</p>
      <span class="lovb-tool-card-cta">Read the markets →</span>
    </a>
    <a class="lovb-tool-card" href="/lovb/roster">
      <div class="lovb-tool-card-eyebrow">// IQ ROSTER</div>
      <h3 class="lovb-tool-card-h">Roster analyzer.</h3>
      <p class="lovb-tool-card-sub">Position-by-position gap analysis for every LOVB team. See where the depth charts are thin — and who could fill them.</p>
      <span class="lovb-tool-card-cta">Find the gaps →</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="lovb-toolkit-footnote">
    <span class="lovb-toolkit-footnote-dot"></span>
    Methodology pages cite every weight and threshold. Open-source approach to pro readiness — no proprietary black box, no affiliate revenue, no "premium tier" gating.
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* LOVB Toolkit cards — match existing lovb-section aesthetic */
  .lovb-toolkit-section { padding-top: 64px; padding-bottom: 64px; }
  .lovb-toolkit-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 18px; margin-top: 36px; }
  .lovb-tool-card { display: block; padding: 28px 26px; background: var(--glass); border: 1px solid var(--glass-edge); border-radius: var(--r-3); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.25s var(--ease-out); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .lovb-tool-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent); opacity: 0.55; transition: opacity 0.25s; }
  .lovb-tool-card:hover { background: var(--glass-2); border-color: var(--glass-edge-2); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .lovb-tool-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .lovb-tool-card-eyebrow { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .lovb-tool-card-h { font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.0; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .lovb-tool-card-h .serif { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: -0.005em; }
  .lovb-tool-card-sub { color: var(--text-2); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .lovb-tool-card-cta { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .lovb-toolkit-footnote { margin-top: 24px; padding: 16px 20px; background: var(--glass); border-left: 2px solid var(--gold); border-radius: 0 var(--r-2) var(--r-2) 0; font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.55; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; }
  .lovb-toolkit-footnote-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--gold); border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--gold-glow); margin-top: 6px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  @media (max-width: 720px) { .lovb-toolkit-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .lovb-tool-card { padding: 22px 20px; } .lovb-tool-card-h { font-size: 26px; } }
</style>

